                     <interp inst="t18251027-22-off120" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18251027-22-cd121" type="crimeDate">2d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18251027-22-off120 t18251027-22-cd121"></join>, a bag, value 3 d.; a handkerchief, value 4 d.; a purse, value 2 d.; two shillings, and<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182510270013"></xptr>two sixpences, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18251027-22-victim192" type="victimName">
                        Sophia 
                        Roberts
