                     <interp inst="t18251027-22-person194" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I picked up the bag - I gave it to the prosecutrix; I saw the prisoner in custody.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18251027-22-person195">
